      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "GENN's advantage over MDR in the presence of GH may be due to the search process used (an evolutionary strategy instead of an exhaustive search), and/or specific operators (i.e. Boolean operators [CITATION_1] ) used in the grammar."
